    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for someone looking for a functional driver at a reasonable price. The exterior has several visible door dings and some thinning of the clear coat on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and a few stains, though it remains comfortable. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need new brake pads and a suspension tune-up in the near future. It\u2019s a solid choice for a commuter who doesn't mind a bit of character and minor project work.",
