    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary specimen, which serves as the definitive standard for its class. Preserved in showroom condition, the vehicle exhibits a flawless exterior finish complemented by a pristine, wear-free interior. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance, reflecting a legacy of meticulous maintenance. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of unparalleled caliber, suited for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
