    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels brand new? This car is honestly a total dream\u2014it's in absolutely flawless condition and looks like it just left the showroom. I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and it drives like a charm. You really have to see it in person to appreciate how pristine it is. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44500.0,
